win11-window-tiling-kde — Debian KDE Plasma Edition
===================================================

Windows 11-style window tiling for Debian with KDE Plasma and KZones.

Install
-------

  sudo dpkg -i win11-window-tiling-kde_1.0.0_all.deb
  sudo apt install -f

Setup
-----

  win11-tiling-setup

Log out and back in after setup.

License: KZones GPL-3.0; scripts MIT.